      "title": "Substitute x equals 36 into the function",
      "content": "We need to find $f(36)$ where $f(x) = 7 + \\sqrt{x}$.<br/>Substitute $x = 36$:<br/>$$f(36) = 7 + \\sqrt{36}$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Evaluate the square root and compute the sum",
      "content": "$\\sqrt{36} = 6$ (since $6^2 = 36$).<br/>Therefore:<br/>$$7 + 6 = 13$$<br/>We enter <strong>13</strong> in the grid."
    }
  ]
}